snippet.textDisplay: This morning I just had the worst and best dream of my life. It was that Mark came to my school (I'm 13) and read a presentation on about his life and work as a YouTuber. I was sitting in class and I here a laugh (Mark's laugh) in the hallway I look over and I see Mark running by. I smile and say ' that can't be him ' go go and ask my teacher if O can go to the bathroom she  says yes (even though I don't have to go) I walk out and see all the 8th grader in lines walking to go to the gym. And im thinking 'no. Way. ' I walk over and I see Mark talking on the stage smiling and doing his thing. I couldn't stop staring. Then my teacher comes walking up to me and says 'I thought you had to go to the bathroom? 'I look at her and almost started crying saying  'I just literally saw my idol!!! ' she smiles..... And that's where it ended..... My dream. I woke up looked around and started crying because that will never happen. I live in a small town in Idaho I'll never meet him. It felt so real!!! I swear!!! I genuinely thought     'I JUST SAW MAKIPLIER!!! ' but nope. And I was so sad. Oh well. I mean I wish I could see him in real life but it most likely won't.
